schools.name: Palm Bay Magnet Senior High School

data.description: Reduced for quick sale! Back in the Market as previous buyer is now relocating to another state. Welcome home to this charming 3 bedrooms, 1.5-bathroom plus flex room. The backyard is an oasis of beautiful vegetation and fruit trees offering relaxation perfect for family gatherings. Location, location, location! It is situated in a very quiet neighborhood, yet close to the Melbourne Mall, FIT college, and the Historic District with a wide variety of shops and restaurants. Only 15 min away from the beautiful Melbourne beaches. It would make a perfect starter or retirement home.
